    "If the user does not have sufficient skills, it is-as beforeessential to seek support from an expert in the respective context.",
    "Overall, this means that free-to-use AI-powered tools like ChatGPT-3.5 have the potential to improve and speed up the research process, but they cannot completely replace human expertise and judgment.",
